description: There’s only one of these emoticons but I quite enjoy it. You could make your own similar ones pretty easily. All you have to do is have an emoticon look uncomfortable with some wide open eyes beside some winking emotes. It’s like the situation is creepy or like somebody is flirting by winking and the other emoticon is not comfortable with it at all. (*⸰‿-) (☉_☉) (-‿◦☀)
title: Two People Winking at Someone and Making them Uncomfortable
